# 🧠 Virtual Assistant Meeting Scheduler (Editable Version)

A simple yet effective meeting scheduler built using **Python (Flask)**, **HTML**, and **CSS**.

---

## ✨ Features

- 📝 Add new meetings with title, date, time, and reminder
- ✏️ Edit existing meetings
- ❌ Delete unwanted meetings
- 🎨 Clean and responsive user interface
- 💻 Built with Python Flask, no database needed

---

## 🗂 Project Structure

virtual_assistant_meeting_scheduler_editable/
├── app.py
├── templates/
│ ├── index.html
│ └── edit.html
├── static/
│ └── style.css
